<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <title>Your SplitSub Magic Link</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #333;
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 20px;
      }
      .header {
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 30px;
      }
      .logo {
        font-size: 24px;
        font-weight: bold;
        color: #2563eb;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
      }
      .magic-link-button {
        display: inline-block;
        background-color: #2563eb;
        color: white;
        padding: 12px 24px;
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 6px;
        font-weight: 500;
        margin: 20px 0;
      }
      .magic-link-button:hover {
        background-color: #1d4ed8;
      }
      .warning {
        background-color: #fef3c7;
        border: 1px solid #f59e0b;
        border-radius: 6px;
        padding: 15px;
        margin: 20px 0;
      }
      .footer {
        margin-top: 30px;
        padding-top: 20px;
        border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
        font-size: 14px;
        color: #6b7280;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="header">
      <div class="logo">SplitSub</div>
      <p>Your secure sign-in link</p>
    </div>

    <p>Hi there!</p>

    <p>You requested a magic link to sign in to your SplitSub account. Click the button below to sign in securely:</p>

    <div style="text-align: center;">
      <a href="<%= @magic_link_url %>" class="magic-link-button">
        Sign in to SplitSub
      </a>
    </div>

    <p>Or copy and paste this link into your browser:</p>
    <p style="word-break: break-all; background-color: #f3f4f6; padding: 10px; border-radius: 4px;">
      <%= @magic_link_url %>
    </p>

    <div class="warning">
      <strong>⚠️ Security Notice:</strong>
      <ul>
        <li>This link will expire in <%= @expires_in_minutes.round %> minutes</li>
        <li>This link can only be used once</li>
        <li>If you didn't request this link, you can safely ignore this email</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
      <p>This email was sent to <%= @user.email_address %></p>
      <p>If you have any questions, please contact our support team.</p>
      <p>&copy; <%= Date.current.year %> SplitSub. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html> 